LIQUID TAGS
LIQUID FILTERS







SEPIA: -sepia-tone 80% 
REDUCE TO 8 COLOR: -dither [Riemersma|FloydSteinberg|None] 
DESATURATE: -quantize Gray -colors 256 
LEVELS/GAMMA (contrast): -level 20% 80% 
COMIX STYLE: -ordered-dither h8x8a (can be combined with color reduction) 
TV SCREEN EFFECT: -virtual-pixel white -distort Barrel "0.2 0.0 0.0 1.0" 
ROTATE: -virtual-pixel white -rotate 2 
OIL PAINT: -paint 4 
COLORIZE: -fill "#18C212" -colorize 20% 
DESATURATE+COLORIZE: -fill "#18C212" -quantize Gray -colors 256 -colorize 20%
TINT (COLORIZE TO EXACT COLOR): -fill "#18C212" -tint 100 
BRIGHTNESS/SATURATION: -modulate 150%,30% 
ADVANCED COMIC STYLE: -modulate 150%,200% -ordered-dither h4x4a BLUR: -gaussian-blur 10,5 
OVERLAY: public/themes/sacfest/images/overlay-foto.png -composite suggestions: 
DISTORT PERSPECTIVE: USE -map TO MAP/COLORIZE IMAGE 
Rounded and Shaped Corners -resize 90% -virtual-pixel white -rotate -2 -ordered-dither h4x4a -crop 120x120-0-0 -resize 90% -virtual-pixel white -rotate %RANDOM% -crop 120x120-0-0




